analysis.title: Global Market Outlook
analysis.content: Neutral regime prevails amid stagflationary decay. The GMS print of 49 confirms tactical neutrality as the fiscal-monetary nexus faces acute headwinds. Decelerating GDP alongside firming inflation triggers a stagflationary impulse, evidenced by the rotation into precious metals and VIX expansion beyond the 20-handle. While credit spread compression persists, the systemic erosion in crypto sentiment and stagnant liquidity vectors mandate a shift toward capital preservation. [MARKET STATUS: DEFENSIVE]

reports.EN: Neutral regime prevails amid stagflationary decay. The GMS print of 49 confirms tactical neutrality as the fiscal-monetary nexus faces acute headwinds. Decelerating GDP alongside firming inflation triggers a stagflationary impulse, evidenced by the rotation into precious metals and VIX expansion beyond the 20-handle. While credit spread compression persists, the systemic erosion in crypto sentiment and stagnant liquidity vectors mandate a shift toward capital preservation. [MARKET STATUS: DEFENSIVE]
reports.ES: El rgimen neutral impera ante el riesgo estanflacionario. El GMS de 49 confirma una postura tctica neutral mientras el nexo fiscal-monetario enfrenta vientos en contra. La desaceleracin del PIB junto con una inflacin del 3% activa un impulso estanflacionario, evidenciado por la rotacin hacia metales preciosos y la expansin del VIX por encima de 20. La erosin del sentimiento cripto y la liquidez estancada exigen priorizar la preservacin de capital. [MARKET STATUS: DEFENSIVE]
reports.ID: Rezim netral mendominasi di tengah tekanan stagflasi. Skor GMS 49 mengonfirmasi netralitas taktis saat neksus fiskal-moneter menghadapi hambatan makro. Melambatnya PDB disertai inflasi 3% memicu impuls stagflasi, terbukti dari rotasi ke logam mulia dan ekspansi VIX melampaui level 20. Meskipun kompresi spread kredit berlanjut, erosi sistemik pada sentimen kripto dan stagnasi likuiditas menuntut pergeseran menuju preservasi modal. [MARKET STATUS: DEFENSIVE]
reports.DE: Neutrales Regime dominiert bei stagflationrem Verfall. Der GMS-Wert von 49 besttigt eine taktische Neutralitt, da der fiskal-monetre Nexus Gegenwind erfhrt. Die BIP-Verlangsamung bei gleichzeitiger Inflationsverfestigung lst stagflationre Impulse aus, sichtbar in der Rotation in Edelmetalle und dem VIX-Anstieg ber 20. Trotz Kreditspread-Kompression erfordern das schwindende Krypto-Sentiment und stagnierende Liquidittsvektoren eine defensive Kapitalerhaltung. [MARKET STATUS: DEFENSIVE]
reports.FR: Le rgime neutre prvaut face au dclin stagflationniste. Le GMS de 49 impose une neutralit tactique alors que le nexus fiscalo-montaire subit des vents contraires. La dclration du PIB et l'inflation  3% dclenchent une impulsion stagflationniste, illustre par la rotation vers les mtaux prcieux et l'envole du VIX au-del de 20. L'rosion systmique du sentiment crypto et la stagnation des vecteurs de liquidit imposent une transition vers la prservation du capital. [MARKET STATUS: DEFENSIVE]
